{
  "stem": "20581.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Levine, ?] which was the general consul for Israel-- I knew him personally-- every time if I needed, I wanted his car to go to a [INAUDIBLE] or something, I used to take this car.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So he says, [INAUDIBLE] [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Levine ?] will give you a visa.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He said, I'll give you a passport.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You could go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He says, you stay in Israel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I'll give you all the money you need.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I guarantee you I'll settle you up-- you'll be-- I'll see to it that you get a good position.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And if you decide later on, you want to come back to the States to go [? to ?] America, he say, you free-- free to do so.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I say, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I don't want to do this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I says, for some reason, I says, I decided I want to go to the States.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And he says, it's OK.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I say, all right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "That's-- it's OK with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But in a way, when I met-- I went [INAUDIBLE] and then my friends, a lot of [? friends ?] come for me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And all, or a lot of people from Berihah, who worked in Berihah, they always telling me, [INAUDIBLE], you would have been OK in Israel.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "You would have a good position there because you were very famous.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "He says, ?] you would have been doing OK in Israel, too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "OK, so--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1950.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "February the 19, 1950.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did all kind of work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] kind of work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I started to work in a factory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I-- yeah, mostly I did, like, a factory work and metal-- sheet metal, until I started my own little business.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have, like, a little-- I had-- itwas pretty good.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
